name: Anushka on working with the Khans
description: After stepping into Bollywood in 2008 Anushka Sharma has worked with Bollywood's three Khans-Shah Rukh, Salman and Aamir, says rather than looking back at her journey and contemplate, she prefers to use the learning to do better.

name: Padmavati TRAILER | Ranveer-Deepika-Shahid's battle
description: We already saw the royal looks of the three leads Ranveer Singh, Deepika Padukone and Shahid Kapoor look nothing less than mesmerizing leaving the audiences awestruck, now the trailer of the film has been released. Taking to twitter the filmmakers shared the trailer video and wrote:

name: SRK's 'Kuch Kuch Hota Hai' made NO SENSE: Karan Johar
description: 'Kuch Kuch Hota Hai', a film that released in 1998, almost 20 years down the line filmmaker Karan Johar feels that the film made no sense. However, on work front, Karan is gearing for 'Ittefaq' that features Sidharth Malhotra and Sonakshi Sinha in the leads. He also has 'Drive' with Sushant Singh Rajput and Jacqueline Fernandez and 'Dragon' with Ranbir Kapoor and Alia Bhatt.

name: Karan BANS Media | No Promotions for Ittefaq
description: 'Ittefaq', a remake of Rajesh Khannas film of the same name sees Sidharth Malhotra and Sonakshi Sinha in fierce avatars as suspects to murders. We also get to see Akshay Khanna in his fierce detective avatar. It is an action-thriller film that revolves around 2 murders-2 suspects and their 2 versions.

name: Salmans sister Arpita excited about hubbys Bollywood debut
description: Superstar Salman Khan's youngest sister Arpita Khan is excited about the Bollywood debut of her husband Aayush Sharma. She tweeted, "I'm so happy and excited for you! I know you will make us all proud. Love you lots Aayush Sharma!"

name: SRKs LOVE for Wifey Gauri Khan | SRK- Gauri PDA Moment
description: Bollywood actor Shah rukh khan, who rules on everyones heart, looks like now he become the Baadshah of his wife Gauri Khan. Recently SRK attended the vogue women of the year award night with none other than his wife Gauri Khan. For the event, where Gauri Khan opted for a traditional chic look and picked a Monisha Jaising sari to nail it, Shah Rukh khan looked dashing in black tuxedo suit.

name: Zaira is the FINEST Hindi film actor: Aamir Khan
description: He has worked with Zaira Wasim in "Dangal" and in the forthcoming project "Secret Superstar". Bollywood star Aamir Khan has praised the child artiste, saying she is the finest actor in the Hindi filmdom now. The actor spoke about working with Zaira when he went to the Global Indian International School (GIIS) in Singapore to promote the film, read a statement.

name: Varun Dhawan- Alia Bhatt TURNS Astronaut
description: Yesterday we saw Varun donned a cowboy look, Alia looks pretty in a red cold shoulder dress. Seeing them pose romantically, we wish for them to star in yet another movie together. But unfortunately there is no movie on the cards as the duo turned astronauts for their upcoming ad campaign called clean initiative. Yes, the couple has came together for an ad campaign.

name: Celebs BLOWN Away by PADMAVATI TRAILER
description: The newly launched trailer of Sanjay Leela Bhansali's "Padmavati" spells grandeur and focuses on the valour of Rajputs, and not any romantic angle between the characters of Padmavati and the medieval-era Delhi ruler Alauddin Khilji.

name: Not Ranveer, Arjun was the first choice for Kapil Dev movie
description: Actor Arjun Kapoor doesn't consider it appropriate to ponder over lost chances. This was evident when he deemed it as "trivial" to discuss whether he regrets not getting a chance to work in Kabir Khan's "1983". Arjun was reportedly considered for the Kabir Khan film on India's victory in the 1983 World Cup. Ranveer Singh has been locked to play the role of Kapil Dev in the movie.

name: 'Judwaa 2' crosses Rs 100 CRORE mark
description: Filmmaker David Dhawans action-comedy film "Judwaa 2", a reboot of the 1997 Salman Khan-starrer "Judwaa", has crossed the Rs 100 crore mark in eight days since its release, the makers have said. Released on September 29, the movie, starring Varun Dhawan, Jacqueline Fernandez and Taapsee Pannu in the lead, minted Rs 4.25 crore on Friday, thus taking its cumulative total to Rs 102.33 crore.

name: Irrfan Khan PRAISES Rajkummar Rao
description: Qarib Qarib Singlle, actor Irrfan Khan's next movie after the 2017 sleeper hit "Hindi Medium", has been locked for release on November 10 and just before that Irrfan praised another talent Rajkummar Rao. During the trailer launch when asked if audience have evolved to content-driven cinema he mentioned how not just his films but Rajkummar's films too have been appreciated, he said:

name: SRK gets Emotional : Kundan Shah reminded me of my mother
description: Veteran Filmmaker Kundan Shah, director of the cult black comedy "Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro" and the romantic drama "Kabhi Haan Kabhi Naa", died on Saturday, a family member said.

name: Kajol seeks BLESSINGS from GODDESS Durga
description: The five-day long festival, which begins from the sixth day of Sharad Navaratri and continues till Vijayadashami has come to its end. On the seventh day of Navratri, the ardent devotee of Goddess Durga, actress Kajol visited a durga pujo pandal to seek the blessings from Durga.

name: Mini Mathur faces Wardrobe MALFUNCTION
description: Filmmaker Kabir Khan's wife and a television host herself Mini Mathur experienced a wardrobe malfunction at the latest event. Present at the announcement of 'Indian's biggest sports film 1983' Mathur faced a little peek-a-boo moment where a part of her inner wear is visible.

name: Karans BIGGEST Birthday GIFT to RANBIR
description: Bollywood Heartthrob Ranbir Kapoor has turned a year older today. The actor already celebrated his birthday with b-town biggies including Shah rukh, alia, aamir and karan johar.

name: Kunal wishes darling wife Soha a very HBday
description: Soha Ali Khan is enjoying the best phase of her life and the first reason is her five days old baby Inaaya Naumi Kemmu, who was born on the auspicious occasion of Mahanavmi. The second reason is after her delivery she is celebrating her birthday on 4th October with her husband kunal Kemmu and family members.

name: Varun Dhawan PROPOSES Princess Alia Bhatt
description: There is no doubt that Varun Dhawan and Alia Bhatt make for a perfect on-screen pair. The duo compliment each others energy and make for a visually compelling pair on the big screen. Their movies Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania and Badrinath ki Dulhaniya are the perfect example to explain their chemistry

name: Hrithik-Kangana FIGHT gets UGLIER, Kangana's sister Rangoli JOINS
description: Just today Hrithik Roshan released an open letter on his twitter where he made some shocking revelation about this controversy with Kangana and now sister Rangoli made some more statements involving Hrithik's ex wife Sussanne Khan. Check here what she said in a series of tweetes:

name: Taimur SPENDS quality time with Daddy Saif sans Kareena
description: Till now, more than his parents Kareena Kapoor khan and Saif ali Khan, Taimur Ali Khan is making news with crying, sleeping, playing with a flower, enjoying his playtime with friends, warmly tugged up in his mothers arms, and with other adorable pictures.

name: CHEF Special Screening for Kareena Kapoor Khan
description: Last seen in Rangoon, now Saif Ali Khan will be seen in his next film Chef. The movie will show Saif as a Chef, who tries to make good food and bond with his son. The movie is ready to hit the big screens on 6th October. Before its release the special screening of the movie was held in Mumbai only for Kareena Kapoor Khan.

name: GST relaxations advanced Diwali celebrations: Modi in Gujarat
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi on Saturday said Diwali had come early because of the relaxation in GST rules that brought some relief to small and medium businesses.

name: Shraddha Kapoor 'bowled over' by Neil Nitin Mukesh
description: Actress Shraddha Kapoor, who is gearing up for her Telugu debut in Prabhas-starrer "Saaho", says she was bowled over by her co-star Neil Nitin Mukesh. Neil had previously praised Shraddha and southern star Prabhas. Neil will reportedly play a villain in "Saaho".

name: Jacqueline will do ACTION in RACE 3 but not a Cop
description: Jacqueline will do ACTION in RACE 3 but not a Cop

name: CONFIRMED: Bobby Joins Salman Jacqueline | RACE 3 CAST
description: Race 3 where Salman Khan and Jacqueline Fernandez will be seen again together has got new entrant and he is none other than Bobby Deol.
